vote.title: An ordinance abandoning portions of a drainage easement, utility and drainage easement and sanitary sewer easement to North End, L.P. (formerly known as Jefferson at the North End, L.P.), the abutting owner, containing a total of approximately 90,185 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Field Street and Nowitzki Way - Revenue: General Fund $7,800.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
